text: Jeon Jong-hyuk (; born 21 March 1996) is a South Korean footballer who plays as goalkeeper for Seongnam FC in K League 1. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:South Korean footballers Category:Seongnam FC players Category:K League 2 players Category:K League 1 players
